class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d26de045e4cfa8e516cb11de84993a640fe962","tid":62552,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:45:51.000Z","msg":"想幫啲真香港人， 例如深水埗啲露宿者。露宿者通常搵啲人少嘅地方， 唔似啲支那獸驚死無人知佢廢咁。"},{"pid":"e68f2d25d79ff7ed480f830ab447cf1ad85f1ca0","tid":62552,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>《簡易程序治罪條例》（第228章）第26A條:<br />\n任何人士在公眾地方、街道或水道乞取或收取施捨，均屬犯罪，定罪後可被處罰款500元及監禁（第一或第二次定罪為一個月，而第三次或其後定罪則為12個月）。</blockquote><br />\n適用於支那獸？"},{"pid":"f8d56f05069108449767069309ae95611a3302ad","tid":62552,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:46:49.000Z","msg":"仲有周街捐錢"},{"pid":"fddb1680cb09a273df271d0889950e184d0d20bb","tid":62552,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以報警既<br />\n差佬一般都係趕走佢，費事自己做咁多嘢<br />\n但啲大陸喱之後會走去第個街口再乞過<br />\n好似打游擊咁</blockquote><br />\n明明食環啲人反而又可以同小販打游擊， 好撚諷刺。"},{"pid":"e1c4172e4378ec03a83252f625ca860f434cd182","tid":62552,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有周街捐錢</blockquote><br />\n呢d係咪無同政府申請"},{"pid":"66c2a6696fc33771e50e401968ba02bfea18ec44","tid":62552,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有周街捐錢</blockquote><br />\n你係唔係講籌錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b82061cb510a7a2685953701bbc474065b8537b","tid":62552,"uid":37979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"我試過有個friend喺facebook上面post咗自己捐錢比兩個人形蜈蚣嘅老人家以為自己做咗善事。比支那怪呃左都唔知， 好白痴。仲以為自己有光環。"},{"pid":"304a74024dea1a91f9c63ca6547d6a035e94b8a3","tid":62552,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比條生路行下"},{"pid":"284b8ae3cf05304