0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"唱唔緊要<br />\n唱黎唱去都係個首<br />\n唱同一首都算<br />\n難聽個下仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafedd1fedff00b88a6e8baa7e61ad5c6a208820","tid":62552,"uid":64550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:19:50.000Z","msg":"一唱歌我就實唔忍 即報警<br />\n雖然其實冇咩用<br />\n當撚下狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf9ad903124ff0ee93a3638678d0381105fa5e3","tid":62552,"uid":69939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌 登打士街豪大大個邊長期有個呀婆係度乞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次同條港女fd行過佢話覺得佢好可憐之後俾左50蚊佢<br />\n即刻俾我屌9佢 我都好可憐又唔見佢俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以介紹我識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果個阿婆 成日跪係地下 又細粒 <br />\n果度人又多 好容易唔小心踢到佢"},{"pid":"df32b8406b7e29b64a9048ad132087fd647b4558","tid":62552,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:31:37.000Z","msg":"元朗朗屏西鐵站至元朗廣場果位末期病人係香港人定大陸人？"},{"pid":"303e3be6c10ff366737eb233e0056d9f6dcc2982","tid":62552,"uid":41127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中環好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次見到有便衣周佢地</blockquote><br />\n周完走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中環果d好撚核突 播佛經有個塊面隻眼好似燒溶左紅卜卜果個 街市入面冇手賣用腳寫毛筆字果個算係咁 最憎d集團成日逼果d成身又爛肉又一粒粒肉丸咁好恐怖既人出黎乞<br />\n尖沙咀班外國人就柒左少少 賣藝都唔願 淨係拎塊紙皮 定佢地都係比集團綁架左"},{"pid":"024e3ffd1fb2e87105c2ae019a8b7a35e9303553","tid":62552,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T07:44:20.000Z","msg":"無人講元朗末期病人既？ 著病人袍，多數係元朗廣場出面天橋訓覺<br />\n重要不斷加價，超霸氣"},{"pid":"280176522ab2750c9c9600cbd8c6127ee6336a06","