islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乞衣是集團式經營的，全部受過training</blockquote><br />\n可惜香港警方唔會跟呢條綫， 以前啲警匪片講到又臥底又咩咁， 而家啲O記便衣真係唔知做咩， 好耐未聽過破咩大案。</blockquote><br />\n而家差佬用黎打壓港豬</blockquote><br />\n所以最好誘導/逼使呢啲集團係差佬/高官屋企附近行乞都唔錯。"},{"pid":"a484b00040f8f9a8b43e77b3983f9bd675748084","tid":62552,"uid":28974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最慘d 唱k 撚咪嘴仲要播黎播去都係個幾首屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你聽哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前尖沙咀出口 有個阿婆唱到鬼食泥咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ffb3433c4f6a4b07dfcaeb4d584cea601ca901","tid":62552,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:57:27.000Z","msg":"我自己就次次都報警嘅，唔該大家都出一份力<br />\n唔好睇到覺得眼冤，行快兩步就當冇事<br />\n警署電話唔係一打就聽，你知黑警要蛇王<br />\n但點都要等到打通，逼佢地派人過去<br />\n<br />\n分區警署電話：<a href=\"http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/contact_us.html#rr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2Fcontact_us.html%23rr&d=MXqbSAbZDu%2FemF4bcT8PWXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d0f6e7df\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/contact_us.html#rr</a>"},{"pid":"716ae0f5d94dfdbef0639a76aa2d406003b49f90","tid":62552,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:59:21.000Z","msg":"基本上以前係旺區先多支那乞衣<br />\n但依家係18區新界九龍冇得避，隨時窮撚屋邨都有幾件"},{"pid":"3db712398f6c8301f734007d954cc1a3f76ae952","tid":62552,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:44:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己就次次都報警嘅，唔該大家都出一份力<br />\n唔好睇到覺得眼冤，行快兩步就當冇事<br />\n警署電話唔係一打就聽，你知黑警要蛇王<br />\n但點都要等到打通，逼佢地派人過去<br />\n<br />\n分區警署電話：<a href=\"http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/contact_us.html#rr\" data-sr-url=\"